ch.iserver.ace.algorithm.text
Class InsertOperation

java.lang.Object
  ch.iserver.ace.algorithm.text.InsertOperation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Operation, Serializable
public class InsertOperation
extends Object
implements Operation

The InsertOperation is used to hold a text together with its position index. The text is to be inserted in the document model.
